{"tid":24671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"買lol ac比個mk仔呃左,有冇巴打可以幫手點告得佢入","createTime":"2016-12-05T16:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T05:56:59.000Z","uid":40348,"like":2,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02fbc37b19f85c4d9dbd47f7c169b26ad7428c68","tid":24671,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"講返背景先,可能長小小 希望巴打們唔好介意<br />\n<br />\n男朋友生日 想買個lol ac 送比佢<br />\n<br />\n我就係vlan討論區,搵到間 700$ 鑽1全英20頁runs<br />\n<br />\nwhatapp左佢 好快就覆<br />\n<br />\n入完數, 佢就話 原來鑽一果個賣左<br />\n<br />\n500$ 要個小號啦 鑽5 20頁 全英 (email 電話未認証)<br />\n<br />\n我又唔知價,好啦,我最後都買左<br />\n<br />\n係交易前 我同佢講,如果買完個ac比人封左/鎖左 就要佢比返兩倍錢我 佢都話ok無問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個交易都好流暢 , 入完數 佢入數 果200再退返比我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但問題係早幾日出現<br />\n<br />\n我男朋友無啦啦話個ac 比人封左 連ggc 都入唔到<br />\n<br />\n我就開始上巴哈搵案例啦<br />\n<br />\n原來條扑街真係用拎返個ac<br />\n<br />\n因為個ac o既個人資料係填佢真人既<br />\n<br />\n所以佢直接同小幫手講 有人爆左佢ac <br />\n<br />\n客服就直接封左個賬號 再等個mk仔 填返d証明書<br />\n<br />\n証明個ac係佢擁有既.就可以直接拎返個ac<br />\n<br />\n而家我諗到既方法只有<br />\n1. 寫信比小幫手 同條mk仔攬炒<br />\n<br />\n2.報警(但唔知告唔告得入)<br />\n不誠實使用電腦? <br />\n詐騙?<br />\n<br />\n上vlan 睇返舊post 都見到條扑街呃好多人 <br />\n估唔到我自己都中招 :(<br />\n<br />\n求大家幫下手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然錢唔係好多,<br />\n但比個mk仔呃真係好唔爽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ipve.com/bbs/viewthread.php?tid=632479&amp;highlight=%E9%BE%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipve.com%2Fbbs%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D632479%26highlight%3D%25E9%25BE%258D&d=qmBiDsg5fPYVZGSn6oWIm5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=00b0a584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ipve.com/bbs/viewthread.php?tid=632479&amp;highlight=%E9%BE%8D</a><br />\n呢個就係其他人比佢呃既post  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993593e1bc243def99b63425e3fea4356f17f063","tid":24671,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:15:28.000Z","msg":"望一望樓主個名<br />\n呃錢黨同5p mk妹黨<br />\nLi登仔會企邊邊呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f76f38abd71e6a8eed507990f5fb277db59854","tid":24671,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:15:34.000Z","msg":"6月到衣家都仲係度，除非一大堆人報案，唔係警察唔會做野"},{"pid":"0a1cc032c2236b7aee8bb42ed8e96dfe5a186249","tid":24671,"uid":8227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"又扑 又表達 好撚難幫你"},{"pid":"4584953c74cc454c1347769579a4bf58ab6f54f4","tid":24671,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>望一望樓主個名&lt;br/&gt;呃錢黨同5p mk妹黨&lt;br/&gt;Li登仔會企邊邊呢&lt;img src=&quot;assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70f845bc85a0c0b6759fa2cb8f2ece72655cc8e","tid":24671,"uid":8227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又扑 又表<span style=\"color: red;\">情</span>好撚難幫你</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8825226fc380fc97ee6e47329577ce14894fa08a","tid":24671,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"年中幾百幾個案啦，警察理鬼你咩遊戲嚟架咋。"},{"pid":"99b5fbc7577d1f8ebd28e355ea0acf852e811633","tid":24671,"uid":8966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:20:07.000Z","msg":"你有無對話記錄 銀行轉帳記錄就報得<br />\n你洗咩諗告佢咩罪，差佬會搞<br />\n不過你預左佢搞好耐，想追返就唔好怕哂時間"},{"pid":"d21e4b1191ea6e21c370ab57ce93dd531da10f44","tid":24671,"uid":16039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"報左都冇人會理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼要十幾個case都係呢條友呃錢 佢地先會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9fdb746d72417d3e051c9c889a827